Title: Aresuke
Description: ["Aresuke is the mascot of Sanyo Broadcasting's radio division (", R, 'adio ', S, 'anyo ', K, "abushikigaisha = RSK = Aresuke). The mascot had a little music video jig that was broadcasted everyday for one year. With the new year bringing in a new video. This ran for 4 years. Along with two musical commercials, Aresuke's limelight remains modest."]
